channel.title: Comments on: Congratulations and Thank You to Michelle Henley

item.title: By: Anneliese Taylor
item.dc:creator: Anneliese Taylor
item.description: Congratulations, Michelle! That's excellent news about your position at SFGH Library, and that we'll still get to interact with you.
item.content:encoded: Congratulations, Michelle! That’s excellent news about your position at SFGH Library, and that we’ll still get to interact with you.

item.title: By: Jim Munson
item.dc:creator: Jim Munson
item.description: I'd like to add my congrats as well. Glad to know that we'll have another friend at SFGH!
item.content:encoded: I’d like to add my congrats as well. Glad to know that we’ll have another friend at SFGH!

item.title: By: Julia Kochi
item.dc:creator: Julia Kochi
item.description: Congratulations, Michelle! I'm glad you'll still be in the extended family.
item.content:encoded: Congratulations, Michelle! I’m glad you’ll still be in the extended family.
